&lt;p&gt;Calamares in its current state can already install a Linux operating system (KaOS, Manjaro and Maui are confirmed to work).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for a system installer for your Linux distribution? Grab Calamares, mix and match any number of Calamares modules (or write your own in Python or C++), throw together some branding, package it up and you are ready to ship!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Look for us in #calamares on chat.freenode.net.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
